<C>__{crystal}
<D>__{what did i say about the fires?}
<C>__{milo}
<D>__{you said "please set fires in my bar". wait, no, that's not right. "please don't set fires in my bar".}
<P>__{(off her look) ok, jeez, you try to}
<D>__{get in the holiday spirit...}
<A>__{he drops the flaming photo to the floor, pours his drink on it, then grinds it to pieces with his shoe.}
<C>__{crystal}
<D>__{shouldn't you be working?}
